              "value": "The Saudi stock market showed strong performance in Q1 2026...\n\nKey Highlights:\n- Banking sector up 15%\n- Energy sector stable\n- Technology sector emerging\n\nInvestment Recommendations:\n1. Focus on banking stocks\n2. Monitor oil prices\n3. Consider tech startups",
